i## Configuration for Linux Systemd-networkd		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iSystemd-networkd is a network management program that comes with		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iSystemd, typically used on devices with fixed network conditions, such		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ias servers. Network Manager is rarely used on these devices.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
